nodes.text: This stormtrooper was stationed on the first Death Star in 0 BBY.
When the Millennium Falcon was captured by the battlestation, Obi-Wan Kenobi heard this stormtrooper respond to KE-829's question about the BT-16.
In the popular non-canon comic series Star Wars: Tag & Bink, it is retconned these two stormtroopers are Tag and Bink.
